dfischer.proxysniffer

Class ProxyDataDump

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.proxysniffer.ProxyDataDumpInfo
      • dfischer.proxysniffer.ProxyDataDump

  • public class ProxyDataDump
extends dfischer.proxysniffer.ProxyDataDumpInfo
    Contains all data of a recorded session.

     ProxyDataDump.getProxyData()
   |
   +-- ProxyDataRecord 1      ---> HttpRequest / HttpResponse
   +-- ProxyDataRecord 2      ---> HttpRequest / HttpResponse
   |   ...
   +-- ProxyDataRecord x      ---> Page Break
   |   ...
   +-- ProxyDataRecord n - 1  ---> HttpRequest / HttpResponse
   +-- ProxyDataRecord n      ---> HttpRequest / HttpResponse
    See Also:
    getProxyData(), ProxyDataRecord, HttpRequest, HttpResponse, writeObject(java.io.DataOutputStream), readObject(java.io.DataInputStream)
